=80=99t suffer losses on all $31 million, the eventual
sales of those works will cut into any profits made this year.  <br/><br/>T=
he current staff reductions were surely planned long before the fall sales.=
 And I=E2=80=99ve heard talk that the new fee structure might not last thro=
ugh the end of this year. What Sotheby=E2=80=99s looks like after the dust =
